name: Wet Work
tooltip:
Wet Work

Krokk wants you to kill Dorinar, Arminon, Endolar, and 12 Ashenvale Scouts.

Speak to Kadrak in Splintertree if you lose your Secret Signal Powder.

Requirements:
- Protector Endolar slain
- Protector Dorinar slain
- Protector Arminon slain
- Ashenvale Scouts defeated x 12
